data.description: Welcome to your cozy starter home just in time for Christmas! This 3 bedroom home has all the space for entertaining with an open floor plan, ample cabinet space, and a bonus room off the kitchen that could be turned into another bedroom! The fenced in yard and covered porch will be your favorite place to toast marshmallows and sip your coffee. schedule your showing today!
